---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---

<StarlightPage
  frontmatter={{
    title: 'Demo Time as a Service',
    description: 'Stop spending days building demos with Demo Time as a Service.',
    tableOfContents: false,
  }}
>
  <div class="service-page">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <header class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Demo Time as a Service</p>
      <h1>Let's make your demos bulletproof.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        <a href="https://eliostruyf.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Elio</a> has been
        done many technical talks and demos over the years. That is why he started Demo Time to perfect
        the demo experience. The service allows you to hand over your repo, and it turns it into a <strong
          >stress-free, scripted Demo Time presentation</strong
        > that you can deliver with confidence.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="button primary" href="#get-started">Get started</a>
        <span class="subtext">Only 10 early-bird slots available.</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    {/* Problem Section */}
    <section class="problem">
      <h2>The Challenge: Why we lose days on demos</h2>
      <p>
        we all know the feeling. You want to tell a great story, but you're stuck fighting with
        broken commands, messy configs, and the fear of a live failure. It's not just
        frustrating—it's a waste of your engineering time.
      </p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Maintenance nightmares</h3>
          <p>You update a feature, and suddenly your old demo script falls apart.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card !mt-0">
          <h3>The narrative gap</h3>
          <p>Great code doesn't always equal a great story. Finding the right flow is hard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Demo anxiety</h3>
          <p>The pressure of "Will this actually work when I'm on stage?" is real.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Scattered notes</h3>
          <p>
            No templates, no structure. Every time you present, it feels like starting from scratch.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Fine-tuning</h3>
          <p>
            Hours spent tweaking code steps, commands, highlights, and practicing your delivery.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>The trust cost</h3>
          <p>A failed demo isn't just awkward. It damages trust and credibility.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Solution Section */}
    <section class="solution">
      <div class="solution-content">
        <h2>The Solution: Demo Time as a Service</h2>
        <p>
          As the creator of Demo Time, Elio knows exactly how to leverage its power. He'll turn your
          project into a seamless, presentation-ready experience.
        </p>
        <ol class="process-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Share your repository</strong> and the story you want to tell.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>We analyze your commits</strong> and generate a Demo Time script.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>You present with confidence</strong>: no typos, no broken commands, no stress.
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          This isn't a video recording. It's a living, code-based demo that evolves with your
          project. That way, you do not have to re-record your demos with every update.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Authority / Trust */}
    <section class="authority">
      <div class="authority-content">
        <h2>Why work with me?</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Elio Struyf</strong> is a Solutions Architect, Microsoft MVP, GitHub Star, and Google
          Developer Expert. He has built tools like Front Matter CMS and Demo Time to help developers
          be more productive. He knows the friction points of technical presentations because he faces
          them too. Let him use that experience to help you shine.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Audience Section */}
    <section class="audience">
      <h2>Who is this for?</h2>
      <p>This service is for teams who need to deliver high-quality technical content at scale.</p>
      <ul class="audience-list">
        <li><strong>Training Platforms</strong> building hands-on developer labs.</li>
        <li><strong>DevRel Teams</strong> showcasing new SDKs and tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Conference Speakers</strong> who need rock-solid workshop materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Corporate Trainers</strong> teaching internal frameworks.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* Pricing Section */}
    <section class="pricing">
      <div class="pricing-card featured">
        <div class="pricing-header">
          <h3>Demo Creation</h3>
          <div class="price">€ 500 <span class="period">/ demo</span></div>
          <p class="badge">Early Bird (First 10 customers)</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li>One demo/presentation (up to 15 mins)</li>
          <li>Based on 1 git repository</li>
          <li>Delivered as a Demo Time script</li>
          <li>2 revision rounds included</li>
          <li>30-minute onboarding session</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="extra-info">Standard turnaround: 5-7 business days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card !mt-0">
        <div class="pricing-header">
          <h3>Expert Coaching</h3>
          <div class="price">€ 200 <span class="period">/ hour</span></div>
          <p class="badge" style="visibility: hidden;">Limited Availability</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li>Review and audit existing demos</li>
          <li>Rewrite complex sections for clarity</li>
          <li>Improve flow, timing, and impact</li>
          <li>Structure narrative for your audience</li>
          <li>Create reusable assets</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Requirements Section */}
    <section class="requirements">
      <h2>Requirements</h2>
      <p>
        To ensure we can create the best demo for you, your repository should meet these criteria:
      </p>
      <ul class="req-list">
        <li>Repository must be Git-based.</li>
        <li>Meaningful commit messages (guidelines provided).</li>
        <li>Each step should be defined with a structured commit message.</li>
        <li>Access provided (public or collaborator).</li>
        <li>1-paragraph description of the story.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">
        <em>Don't meet these? We can provide guidance or coaching to help you prepare.</em>
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* FAQ Section */}
    <section class="faq">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div>
          <strong>Do I need to be a Demo Time user already?</strong>
          <p>No. We'll provide everything you need to get started, including onboarding.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>What if my git history is messy?</strong>
          <p>We provide guidelines. If you need help cleaning it up, we offer coaching.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>Can you demo third-party products?</strong>
          <p>
            Not yet. This service is for code-based demos in VS Code where you control the repo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>What format do I receive?</strong>
          <p>You'll receive a Demo Time script file (YAML), fully configured and ready to use.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* CTA Section */}
    <section id="get-started">
      <h2>Ready to reclaim your time?</h2>
      <p>We're launching with a limited pilot program. Lock in the € 500 early bird price.</p>

      <form
        id="interestForm"
        class="interest-form"
        action="https://formbold.com/s/obkNp"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="apiKey" value="sf_2g9h855e668na16n94fl0lh4" />
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Demo Time Service Interest" />
        <input type="hidden" name="replyTo" value="@replyEmail" />
        <input type="text" name="honeypot" style="display: none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Full Name</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Doe" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@example.com" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="organization">Organization/Company</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input
              type="text"
              id="organization"
              name="organization"
              placeholder="Demo Time, etc."
              required
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="role">Your Role</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="role" name="role" required>
              <option value="">Select your role...</option>
              <option value="training-manager">Training Manager</option>
              <option value="devrel">Developer Relations</option>
              <option value="content-creator">Content Creator</option>
              <option value="conference-organizer">Conference Organizer</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Which services are you interested in?</label>
          <div class="checkbox-group">
            <label class="checkbox-label">
              <input type="checkbox" name="$services" value="creation" checked />
              Demo creation service (€ 500)
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-label">
              <input type="checkbox" name="$services" value="coaching" />
              Expert coaching (€ 200/hour)
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="demoDescription"
            >What types of demos does your organization create? (1-2 sentences)</label
          >
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="demoDescription"
              name="demoDescription"
              rows="2"
              placeholder="e.g., Hands-on labs for developer training, product feature demonstrations, conference workshops"
              required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="frequency">How many demos does your team create per quarter?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="frequency" name="frequency" required>
              <option value="">Select quantity...</option>
              <option value="1-5">1-5 demos</option>
              <option value="6-10">6-10 demos</option>
              <option value="11-20">11-20 demos</option>
              <option value="20+">20+ demos</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="challenge">What's your biggest challenge with demo creation right now?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="challenge"
              name="challenge"
              rows="2"
              placeholder="e.g., Takes too long to create, demos break during live sessions, hard to maintain when product updates"
              required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="willingness">Is € 500 per demo within your budget?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="willingness" name="willingness" required>
              <option value="">Select answer...</option>
              <option value="yes">Yes, this is reasonable</option>
              <option value="need-approval">Yes, but need approval</option>
              <option value="multiple">Yes, interested in ordering multiple demos</option>
              <option value="too-high">This seems too high</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Additional questions or comments (Optional)</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="3"
              placeholder="Any questions or specific requirements?"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6Lct-gkrAAAAANXSF_L-hUZUyP-pF4oWzyO0M4jL"></div>

        <script src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js" is:inline></script>

        <button id="submitButton" type="submit" class="button primary full-width">
          Join the Waitlist
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>
          <strong>Questions?</strong> Reach out at <a href="mailto:elio@struyfconsulting.be"
            >elio@struyfconsulting.be</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>Let's make demos less stressful and more impactful—together!</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</StarlightPage>

<style>
  :root {
    --sl-content-width: 50rem;

    .main-pane .content-panel:first-child {
      display: none !important;
    }
  }

  .service-page {
    max-width: 50rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .subtext {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .pillars {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(14rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillars div {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    margin-top: 0 !important;
  }

  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  .card p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
  }

  .pricing {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    position: relative;
  }

  .pricing-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing-header h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--sl-color-accent-low);
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .features-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .features-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
  }

  .features-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .extra-info {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-3);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .audience-list,
  .req-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .audience-list li,
  .req-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(20rem, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-grid strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
  }

  .faq-grid p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .process-list {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .process-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Form */
  .interest-form {
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  input[type='text'],
  input[type='email'],
  textarea,
  select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-4);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-black);
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  input:focus,
  textarea:focus,
  select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--sl-color-accent-low);
  }

  select {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checkbox-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .checkbox-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: normal;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checkbox-label input {
    margin: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button.primary {
    background: rgb(255 212 59 / var(--tw-bg-opacity, 1)) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-text-accent);
    color: #000;
  }

  .button.primary:hover {
    color: #000;
    background-color: rgb(255 212 59 / 0.8) !important;
  }

  .button.full-width {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .contact-info {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .g-recaptcha {
    div,
    iframe {
      height: 78px !important;
    }
  }
</style>
